reviewText:
The delivery of this item was very good. There was something to know that i wonna tell
that on this dvd you've find only a appearance of Little Richard from the movie
"Keep On Rockin' directed of D.A. Pennebaker. It was filmed in Canada i think.
I didn't know and i haven't find a complete film, on dvd, of this movie with all the
actors and they are: Chuck Berry, Bo Diddley, Jimi Hendrix, Janis Joplin, John Lennon and
Yoko Ono (scenes were deleted) and Jerry Lee Lewis. Can someone tell where i can find a
complete dvd of this movie. I am therockman11.
